sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Chalice API
    participant S3 as S3
    participant Rek as Rekognition
    participant Tr as Translate
    participant Pol as Polly

    User->>FE: Select image + click run
    FE->>API: POST /images (base64 file)
    API->>S3: put_object(image)
    API-->>FE: imageId + imageUrl

    FE->>API: POST /images/{id}/speak-text
    API->>Rek: detect_text(image in S3)
    Rek-->>API: detected lines
    loop each high-confidence line
        API->>Tr: translate_text
        Tr-->>API: translated text
    end
    API->>Pol: synthesize_speech(full text)
    Pol-->>API: MP3 bytes
    API->>S3: put_object(audio mp3)
    API-->>FE: translatedText + audioFileUrl
    FE-->>User: Display text + play audio
